        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Panchayat Samiti Nandishala Jan Sahbhagita Yojana&amp;quot;, launched in 2021-22, by the Animal Husbandry Department, Rajasthan, aims to support the construction of permanent infrastructure for the shelter of stray male cattle in each Panchayat Samiti. The scheme provides financial assistance for Nandishala.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - One-time assistance of 90% of the total construction cost.\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The \"Panchayat Samiti Nandishala Jan Sahbhagita Yojana\" was initiated to provide shelter for stray male cattle by constructing infrastructure in Panchayat Samitis.",
