      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. Eligible entities include local bodies, Panchayati Raj institutions, registered trusts, NGOs, and government-recognized institutions.\n   1. The organization must have been operational for at least 3 years.\n   1. Ownership of 20 bighas of private land to sustain 250 male cattle.\n   1. Minimum of 3 years of experience in operating a cattle shelter or similar activities.\n   1. Availability of 10% contribution towards the project cost.\n\n",
